"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"**PERI金融是一个基于Polkadot的跨链创新合成资产发行和衍生品市场协议**\\n\\n**代币已经上线了，撸一下测试竞赛吧，体验就行了**\\n\\n[https://medium.com/perifinance/peri-dex-testnet-pynths-trading-competition-81f9f1b2b2e0](https://medium.com/perifinance/peri-dex-testnet-pynths-trading-competition-81f9f1b2b2e0)\\n\\n**这是他们的官方竞赛文章，总得来说交互过程还是挺复杂的，以下是教程：**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/i2LhpG15w3B7TUUYEfKW9.png?height=308&width=1309)\\n\\n**切换到Moonbase测试网，然后去官方discord领水**\\n\\n[https://discord.gg/vFN4VShU](https://discord.gg/vFN4VShU)\\n\\n**找到这个频道进去领水**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/IVnWEEn9CV-AaZQKjG-HV.png?height=136&width=232)\\n\\n**发送  !faucet send 0x00000000000(你的地址)**\\n\\n**然后去下面这个网址领取PERI测试代币，记得切换成Moonbase主网**\\n\\n[https://staking.peri.finance/#/stake](https://staking.peri.finance/#/stake)\\n\\n[https://staking.peri.finance/#/stake](https://staking.peri.finance/#/stake)\\n\\n[https://staking.peri.finance/](https://staking.peri.finance/)\\n\\n**0xf2585216d44d8cea1c6a07f1b9e25a232c3c2971   这是PERI代币测试网合约地址**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/o8Ud4nnNfyNExJP_VbL3k.png?height=864&width=1597)\\n\\n**领完之后要全部staking进去才能换pusd出来，去MINT那边max全部质押**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/GndVUSOr1v7LlLpItIjMX.png?height=440&width=1057)\\n\\n**差不多能mint出来130多个pusd，然后去dex交易5次**\\n\\n[https://dex.peri.finance/exchange](https://dex.peri.finance/exchange)\\n\\n**最后填写测试表单**\\n\\n[https://forms.gle/dMN7hUWdfq8uYgbX7](https://forms.gle/dMN7hUWdfq8uYgbX7)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641465523,\"title\":\"PERI Finance测试交互（填表参与测试竞赛）\"},\"digest\":\"2NxGXMdmfFWe4PqGncDTqp4XUNZGwsjZrWDUGWigOh0\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xF703A4ADeD9797587e795eE12862dc3Bab7F8146\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"34koQTFrzRknulc-mbdwin8KtOu3h15Pd0PS6iCXv38\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"e0-VEyCf2_ODzW0WXjhsYXVptZ01HUk8V4AjS4vu6t0\\\"}\",